amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-height=\"720\" data-width=\"1280\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"542231631\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"PxrCamera_LensDisrt_Y_minus.jpg\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/jpeg\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"542231607\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"1\" data-media-id=\"bc6f8c4f-bc36-4d5f-933a-e0551349d7b6\" data-media-type=\"file\" srcset=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/542231607/PxrCamera_LensDisrt_Y_minus.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754330715879&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=1280&amp;height=720 2x, https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/542231607/PxrCamera_LensDisrt_Y_minus.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754330715879&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=666&amp;height=374 1x\"></span></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"columnLayout fixed-width\" data-layout=\"fixed-width\">\n<div class=\"cell normal\" data-type=\"normal\">\n<div class=\"innerCell\">\n<p /><p /><p><strong>Anamorphic Squeeze</strong></p><p>Anamorphic lens squeeze. Values greater than one decrease the effect of the lens distortion in the X direction. Values less than one increase it.</p><p /><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-center\" alt=\"PxrCamera_LensDisrt_radial1_.jpg\" width=\"998\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/542231607/PxrCamera_LensDisrt_radial1_.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754330715878&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=998&amp;height=561\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/542231607/PxrCamera_LensDisrt_radial1_.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754330715878&amp;cacheVersio